snippet.title: Magic Inn - Official Gameplay Trailer | Women-Led Games x TGA 2024
snippet.description: Check out gameplay from Magic Inn in this trailer for upcoming tavern life simulator game. Take on the role of an exiled wizard-turned-innkeeper, overseeing everything from menus, rooms, guests, and staff in a fully magical customizable inn. Engage in card battles to spark conversations and foster relationships with guests. Magic Inn will be available on PC (Steam) on January 20, 2025.
